headline: GTA Online
subtitle: A FESTIVE PRESENT
content: On the first day of the holiday, my true love gave to me: One Festive Beerhat, twenty Firework Rockets, a pocket full of Snacks, five Proximity Mines, one Firework Launcher, twenty-five Sticky Bombs, a set of Full Armor, twenty-five Grenades, ten Molotovs, and a Candy Cane for bashing in heads.
